text: Deloche may refer to: ==Surname== * Alain Deloche, (born 1940), French cardiac surgeon and founder of the Chain of Hope * Campocasso (1833–1908), born Auguste Deloche, director of French theater * Maximin Deloche (1817–1900), French historian and numismatist, member of the Société des Antiquaires de France * Pierre Julien Deloche (born 1982), French archer * Robert Deloche (1909–1988), furrier, trade unionist, politician in France and Algeria ==See also== * Loche (disambiguation) * Loches, a commune in central France * Loché, an associated commune of Mâcon, France * Loch (disambiguation)
title: Deloche
